snippet.title: International Basketball Manager 23 Trailer
snippet.description:
International Basketball Manager 23 will be available from December 1st 2022 on Steam, Play Store and App Store.  

In this new edition, UPLAY Basketball has responded to the community and will provide new and innovative tools that promise to make International Basketball Manager 23 the deepest and most detailed basketball game in the world.
